## ğŸ”§ Konfiguration Ã¤ndern

**Grafana Passwort** â†’ `docker-compose.yml`
```yaml
GF_SECURITY_ADMIN_PASSWORD=NeuesPasswort
```
Dann: `docker-compose restart grafana`

**Prometheus Scrape-Intervall** â†’ `prometheus/prometheus.yml`
```yaml
scrape_interval: 15s
```
Dann: `docker-compose restart prometheus`

**Go-App Port** â†’ `docker-compose.yml` + `Dockerfile`
```yaml
ports: ["9999:9999"]
PORT=9999
```
Dann: `docker-compose build && docker-compose up -d`

## ğŸ› Probleme

**Port vergeben?**
```bash
sudo lsof -i :3000      # Welcher Prozess?
sudo kill -9 <PID>      # Beenden
```

**Grafana Login fehlgeschlagen?**
```bash
docker-compose restart grafana
docker-compose logs grafana | tail -20
```

**Container starten nicht?**
```bash
docker-compose down -v
docker-compose build --no-cache
docker-compose up -d
```

**WSL Permission Denied?**
```bash
sudo usermod -aG docker $USER
newgrp docker
```

## ğŸ“ˆ Neue Metriken hinzufÃ¼gen

Bearbeite `main.go`:
```go
counter := prometheus.NewGauge(prometheus.GaugeOpts{
    Name: "neue_metrik",
    Help: "Beschreibung",
})
reg.MustRegister(counter)
```

Dann: `docker-compose build && docker-compose up -d`

